activityByWeekAsFractionOfOwn.title: Relative Activity Compared to Self

Dots represent student activity. Bigger dots indicate more activity relative to that student's 
                      activity during the course term.
activityByWeekAsFractionOfOwn.tooltip:
Dots represent student activity. Bigger dots indicate more activity relative to that student's 
                      activity during the course term.

activityByWeekAsFractionOfTotal.title: Relative Activity Compared to Other Students in Class

activityByWeekAsFractionOfTotal.tooltip: Dots represent student activity. Bigger dots indicate more activity.

timeOnTaskComparativeDistribution.title: Activity by Participant
timeOnTaskComparativeDistribution.legend: Dots appear darker when students are more active.
timeOnTaskComparativeDistribution.tooltip: Dots appear darker when students are more active.

studentList.title: Activity Metrics
studentList.legend: A small number for regularity means, that there is a regular pattern.

activityLevelTimeline.title: Course Activity by Date
activityLevelTimeline.legend:
This graph shows total daily time spent in the course (blue line), the 
                      forecasted activity levels (dotted line), and the estimated potential range in 
                      active hours (thick gray line).

This graph shows total daily time spent in the course (blue line), the

activityCalendarHeatmap.tooltip: Color shade indicates number of persons active on that day.
